<p>The output should help the field team act faster, not read longer. Job purpose. Prior history. Known constraints. Open risks. Recommended checks on arrival. Missing information worth confirming. That kind of structure helps technicians, dispatchers, and service managers line up around the same job reality before the first call from the field starts rebuilding context manually.</p>
